### =====================================================================
### 竞赛通 API 测试文件 (IntelliJ HTTP Client 格式)
### =====================================================================
### 用法:
###   1. IntelliJ IDEA 直接打开本文件
###   2. 文件顶部点击「Examples」选环境(dev/prod)
###   3. 每个 ### 块左侧有绿色三角,点击 Run 即可
###   4. 上一个 ### 块的响应可被 {{变量名}} 引用 (注意 client.global.set)
### =====================================================================

### --- 环境变量 (顶部声明,所有请求复用) ---
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@contentType = application/json

### =====================================================================
### 模块 A: jst-user 认证与资料 (5 接口)
### =====================================================================

### A1. Mock 登录测试用户 1001 (fixture: 测试_张妈妈)
### 期望: 200, 返回 token + 用户信息, isNewUser=false
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/wx/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "MOCK_1001"
}

> {%
client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.data.token);
client.global.set("user_id", response.body.data.userInfo.userId);
client.test("登录成功", function() {
    client.assert(response.status === 200, "状态码应为 200");
    client.assert(response.body.code === 200, "业务码应为 200");
    client.assert(response.body.data.token !== null, "token 不能为空");
    client.assert(response.body.data.userInfo.userId === 1001, "userId 应为 1001");
});
%}

### A2. 用上一步 token 调 profile
### 期望: 200, 返回完整用户资料(脱敏)
GET {{baseUrl}}/jst/wx/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

> {%
client.test("获取资料成功", function() {
    client.assert(response.status === 200);
    client.assert(response.body.data.userId === 1001);
    client.assert(response.body.data.mobileMasked.includes("****"), "手机号必须脱敏");
});
%}

### A3. 更新昵称
PUT {{baseUrl}}/jst/wx/user/profile
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "nickname": "测试_张妈妈_新昵称"
}

> {%
client.test("更新成功", function() {
    client.assert(response.status === 200);
    client.assert(response.body.code === 200);
});
%}

### A4. 全新用户注册 (新 openid)
### 期望: isNewUser=true, 自动创建 jst_user
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/wx/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "MOCK_99999"
}

> {%
client.test("新用户注册", function() {
    client.assert(response.status === 200);
    client.assert(response.body.data.isNewUser === true, "应是新用户");
    client.assert(response.body.data.userInfo.phoneBound === false, "新用户未绑手机");
});
%}

### A5. 登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/wx/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}


### =====================================================================
### 模块 B: jst-user 临时档案认领 (4 接口)
### 前置: 99-test-fixtures.sql 已导入,且重新登录获得新 token
### =====================================================================

### B0. 重新登录(因为 A5 已登出)
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/wx/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "MOCK_1001"
}

> {%
client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.data.token);
%}

### B1. 查我的参赛档案 (应有 1 个: 张小红, fixture 3004)
GET {{baseUrl}}/jst/wx/participant/my
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

> {%
client.test("我的档案列表", function() {
    client.assert(response.status === 200);
    client.assert(Array.isArray(response.body.data), "应返回数组");
    // fixture 中已认领的 3004 张小红
    var found = response.body.data.find(p => p.participantId === 3004);
    client.assert(found, "应包含 fixture 中的 3004 张小红");
    client.assert(found.name === "测试_张小红");
});
%}

### B2. 主动认领临时档案 3001 (张小明)
### 期望: SM-14 跃迁 unclaimed → manual_claimed
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/wx/participant/claim?participantId=3001
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

> {%
client.test("认领成功", function() {
    client.assert(response.status === 200);
    client.assert(response.body.data.participantId === 3001);
    client.assert(response.body.data.userId === 1001);
});
%}

### B3. 重复认领 3001 (应失败,状态机非法跃迁 manual_claimed → manual_claimed)
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/wx/participant/claim?participantId=3001
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

> {%
client.test("重复认领应失败", function() {
    // 业务异常: code != 200
    client.assert(response.body.code !== 200, "重复认领应被拒绝");
});
%}

### B4. 查档案详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/jst/wx/participant/3001
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

> {%
client.test("详情查询", function() {
    client.assert(response.status === 200);
    client.assert(response.body.data.participantId === 3001);
});
%}

### B5. 跨用户越权测试 (3001 已被 1001 认领,新用户登录看 3001 应 403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/wx/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "MOCK_1002"
}

> {%
client.global.set("other_token", response.body.data.token);
%}

### B6. 用 1002 的 token 看 3001 的详情 (应 403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/jst/wx/participant/3001
Authorization: Bearer {{other_token}}

> {%
client.test("越权防御", function() {
    client.assert(response.body.code !== 200, "其他用户不应能看到");
});
%}


